Commentary Text: Tushar Deshpande to Rahane, FOUR, that's vintage Rahane. Trademark Rahane too. Just a lean forward and with minimal footwork lets the hands do the rest. He drives superbly wide of mid-off and it's as pleasing a shot as they come

Commentary Text: Tushar Deshpande to Rahane, 2 runs, Rahane and KKR are away. Just short of fine-leg. Short of a length on the hips, Rahane whips beautifully but in the air, Dube does well to get the body in front as he dives, bounces short and he prevents the boundary
